description: Two men will appear in court later after the fatal stabbing of Jordan Hogg in Middlesbrough.
title: Two charged with murdering Jordan Hogg, 28, in Middlesbrough
title_page: Two charged with murdering Jordan Hogg, 28, in Middlesbrough - BBC News
maintext:
Two men have been charged with murder after a 28-year-old man was fatally stabbed.
Jordan Hogg, 28, died in Fonteyn Court in Hemlington, Middlesbrough, shortly after midnight on Friday.
A 43-year-old man was charged with murder and possession of a bladed article and a 27-year-old man was charged with murder and possession of an offensive weapon.
Both were remanded into custody and are due to appear at Teesside Magistrates' Court.
